OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781168735
OL,3,CTeenage girl arrested after school
OL,4,Cstabbing detained under Mental Health
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FA 14-year-old girl who was arrested
OL,8,Fafter a stabbing at a school in
OL,9,FManchester has been detained under the
OL,10,FMental Health Act.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to the Co-op
OL,13,FAcademy on Plant Hill Road, Blackley
OL,14,Fyesterday (Tuesday 9 June 2026).
OL,16,FTwo pupils and a member of staff were
OL,17,Fstabbed. All three were taken to
OL,18,Fhospital and have now been discharged.
OL,20,FPolice arrested the girl on suspicion
OL,21,Fof section 18 assault.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
