PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781168735
OL,3,CTeenage girl arrested after school
OL,4,Cstabbing detained under Mental Health
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FThe trust which runs the school say
OL,8,Fstaff "acted bravely" to quickly
OL,9,Fdetain a girl before Police arrived.
OL,11,FIt is understood that the school were
OL,12,Fput into lockdown after the incident.
OL,14,FChief Inspector Jon Shilvock from
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police said: "Our
OL,16,Finvestigation has continued at pace
OL,17,Fsince yesterday morning when we were
OL,18,Ffirst made aware of the incident.
OL,26,@wD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781168735
OL,3,CTeenage girl arrested after school
OL,4,Cstabbing detained under Mental Health
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with those that were
OL,8,Finjured and were caught up in the
OL,9,Fincident. Whilst the physical injuries
OL,10,Fwere not believed to be serious, we
OL,11,Fknow the impact to those that were
OL,12,Finvolved or were witnesses to this
OL,13,Fwill be significant, and we want to
OL,14,Freassure our community we are taking
OL,15,Fthis very seriously.
OL,17,F"As our investigation progresses, we
OL,18,Fare aware that names relating to the
OL,19,Fincident are being circulated on
OL,20,Fsocial media which are unhelpful for
OL,21,Fthe investigation.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781168735
OL,3,CTeenage girl arrested after school
OL,4,Cstabbing detained under Mental Health
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"This is also causing concern with the
OL,8,Fvictims and those that have been
OL,9,Fimpacted therefore we would stress
OL,10,Fthat people do not speculate regarding
OL,11,Fthis incident.
OL,13,F"Officers will remain in and around
OL,14,Fthe area to provide support to ensure
OL,15,Fstaff, students and the wider
OL,16,Fcommunity feel safe. If you have any
OL,17,Fconcerns, please speak to our officers
OL,18,Fwho are there to support you."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@^O]
